HEADWORD: fall webworm
<hw>fall webworm</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The larva
of any moth of the genus <gen>Hyphantria</gen>, which spins a web around
the foliage on which it feeds.</def>⟦br⟧
